          "Title": "ADVANCE OPEN WATER",
          "Description": "Take it to the next level",
          "Content": "<h2 style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\">advanced OPEN WATER COURSE</h2><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><iframe frameborder=\"0\" src=\"//www.youtube.com/embed/tWPGi52nkHg\" width=\"640\" height=\"360\" class=\"note-video-clip\"></iframe><br></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><table class=\"table table-bordered\"><tbody><tr><td><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">Your Next Dive Adventure</span></div><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: left;\"><br></div><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; text-align: left;\">As a certified scuba diver you've already experienced the thrill of exploring parts of the underwater world, but know there's more to discover. Whether you're looking for new dive adventures, to improve your scuba skills, or both at once, taking another PADI dive course will help you gain more confidence and meet more dive buddies.</div><div style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></div></div></td><td><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">PADI Advanced Open Water Diver Course</span></div><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\"><br></div><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif;\">In the PADI Advanced Open Water Diver course, there's a long list of scuba specialty dives to try. Fish identification, boat diving, altitude diving, drift diving, sidemount diving, search and recovery, wreck diving, plus about 12 more. You do five different dives all under the expert guidance of your PADI Instructor. &nbsp;</div><div style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></div></div><div style=\"font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; font-size: medium; font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\"><br></div></td></tr></tbody></table><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal;\">To sign up for PADI elearning </span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal;\"><b>Advanced Open Water</b></span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal;\"> course please click on the banner below</span><br></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><br></p><p style=\"font-family: &quot;Open Sans&quot;, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: 6px; text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.padi.com/elearning-scuba-registration/default.aspx?irra=36284&amp;CourseType=aow\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"img-thumbnail\" style=\"width: 650px;\" src=\"https://www.dropbox.com/s/qqu76m8ryppn0hx/Open%20Water%20Static%20Banner%208.jpg?raw=1\"></a><br></p>",
